snippet.title: Poison Control - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/poison-control

When a mysterious phenomenon causes spirits to become trapped within poisonous manifestations of their own personal despair, only the haughty Poisonette and her amnesiac Soul Mate can purify them. Venture through the different Belles' Hells to defeat enemies, learn the stories of fallen souls and other Poisonettes, and fight your way to Heaven in this stylishly twisted action shooter!

Coming Early 2021 to Nintendo Switch and PS4.

#PoisonControl #NISAmerica
